<http://www.semanticweb.org/usuario1/ontologies/2025/4/untitled-ontology-2#con0116> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
